      • alt

        public static org.openqa.selenium.By alt(String alt)
        Find an image by the "alt" attribute value. Lot's of images have an alt attribute providing alternate text to display. Use this method to find an image by this text.
        Parameters:
        alt - The text of the alt attribute to search for.
        Returns:
        a By instance that finds web elements in web driver.
